widgets_values: If you have Triton and SageAttention installed, connect the Torch Compile Args to gain roughly a 30% speed boost. If these are not available, leave the WAN 2.2 Animate Torch Compile Settings disconnected (disable with Ctrl+B) and set attention_mode to sdpa in the WAN 2.2 Animate Model Loader.
Connect `loaded_fps` to `Set_fps` instead of `source_fps` if you changed the `force_rate` in the `Load Video` node
To use the background/surroundings of the reference image, disable both Get_mask and Get_background_image connected to the WanVideo Animate Embeds.
